GS can incorporate any kind of\nSI violation and can produce nSI realizations efficiently.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2013 18:26:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Apr 2015 14:45:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-04-27"}
