 be coupled from below with oriented site\npercolation. Our results re-open the study of critical probabilities in\nbootstrap percolation on infinite lattices, and they allow one to ask many\nquestions of subcritical bootstrap percolation models that are typically asked\nof site or bond percolation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2013 20:55:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Sep 2014 20:13:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-10"}
