hat finite-sized menu\ncannot guarantee any positive fraction of optimal revenue for correlated\nvaluation distributions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Nov 2013 07:03:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 29 Apr 2014 06:38:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-30"}
